// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2462 — Mass File Rename (thegentlemen)
// Status: test | Level: high | ID: 2f8610eb-3967-572c-8418-862b446d6045

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
